{"word":"σκαφίς","slug":"σκαφίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σκαφίς</b></el> <el>(σκᾰφίς, ίδος, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Diminutive'>Dim.</a> of <a href='S:σκάφη'><el>σκάφη</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Diminutive'>Dim.</a> of <el>σκάφη</el>: <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a bowl, milk-pail</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>:— <i>a pot</i> for honey, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a small boat, skiff, canoe</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a shovel</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}